Text.SourceString: Hey there, new face!
Text.LocalizedString: Hey there, new face!

Text.SourceString: So you can swim, huh? Interesting.
Text.LocalizedString: So you can swim, huh? Interesting.

Text.SourceString: These currents are great for my plants. They bring over a lot of nutrients.
Text.LocalizedString: These currents are great for my plants. They bring over a lot of nutrients.

Text.SourceString: The currents feel quite lively today, don't they?
Text.LocalizedString: The currents feel quite lively today, don't they?

Text.SourceString: The water’s warm today, kinda like an oceanic hot tub, minus the bubble jets.//<portrait=normal>Perfect for the sea anemones in the garden.
Text.LocalizedString: The water’s warm today, kinda like an oceanic hot tub, minus the bubble jets.//<portrait=normal>Perfect for the sea anemones in the garden.

Text.SourceString: This cooler current reminds me of the old tales from the deep trenches
Text.LocalizedString: This cooler current reminds me of the old tales from the deep trenches

Text.SourceString: Maybe the ocean's having its <Italic>frozen</> moment. Let it go, right?
Text.LocalizedString: Maybe the ocean's having its <Italic>frozen</> moment. Let it go, right?

Text.SourceString: Winter seaweeds have such rich flavors. I've been experimenting with some new recipes!
Text.LocalizedString: Winter seaweeds have such rich flavors. I've been experimenting with some new recipes!

Text.SourceString: Spring's currents bring the best crafting materials. Those iridescent shells are in this year.//I'm all geared up for some shell shopping.
Text.LocalizedString: Spring's currents bring the best crafting materials. Those iridescent shells are in this year.//I'm all geared up for some shell shopping.

Text.SourceString: Denali was quite the handful growing up, always curious.//The apple doesn't fall far from the coral, as they say. A total mini-me.
Text.LocalizedString: Denali was quite the handful growing up, always curious.//The apple doesn't fall far from the coral, as they say. A total mini-me.

Text.SourceString: I've been weaving some new patterns into the seaweed textiles. It's always refreshing to learn something new.
Text.LocalizedString: I've been weaving some new patterns into the seaweed textiles. It's always refreshing to learn something new.

Text.SourceString: There's something truly special about this community. Everyone's so supportive, it warms my heart.
Text.LocalizedString: There's something truly special about this community. Everyone's so supportive, it warms my heart.

Text.SourceString: You know, there's a secret recipe to my seaweed soup. But, between you and me, it's all about the love you put into it.
Text.LocalizedString: You know, there's a secret recipe to my seaweed soup. But, between you and me, it's all about the love you put into it.

Text.SourceString: I overheard some merfolk talking about the latest underwater dance craze. Made me want to shake my tail fin and join in.
Text.LocalizedString: I overheard some merfolk talking about the latest underwater dance craze. Made me want to shake my tail fin and join in.

Text.SourceString: Sometimes, when the currents are just right, Tahat and I take a swim up to the surface.//<portrait=happy>The view of the night sky is simply breathtaking.
Text.LocalizedString: Sometimes, when the currents are just right, Tahat and I take a swim up to the surface.//<portrait=happy>The view of the night sky is simply breathtaking.

Text.SourceString: Do you know? <NPCName>Denali</> once tried to make her own shell castle. Ambition starts young, I guess.
Text.LocalizedString: Do you know? <NPCName>Denali</> once tried to make her own shell castle. Ambition starts young, I guess.

Text.SourceString: I've been teaching <NPCName>Denali</> some of my old crafting tricks. It's our little mother-daughter bonding time.//<portrait=concerned>But, you know, she's got her sights set on keeping the Kingdom safe.
Text.LocalizedString: I've been teaching <NPCName>Denali</> some of my old crafting tricks. It's our little mother-daughter bonding time.//<portrait=concerned>But, you know, she's got her sights set on keeping the Kingdom safe.

Text.SourceString: That's where her heart is. All I can do is cheer her on from the sidelines.
Text.LocalizedString: That's where her heart is. All I can do is cheer her on from the sidelines.

Text.SourceString: Every now and then, I catch <NPCName>Denali</> singing a lullaby. Warms my heart.
Text.LocalizedString: Every now and then, I catch <NPCName>Denali</> singing a lullaby. Warms my heart.

Text.SourceString: When she was little, <NPCName>Denali</> and I would race across the coral maze. She always won, cheeky girl!
Text.LocalizedString: When she was little, <NPCName>Denali</> and I would race across the coral maze. She always won, cheeky girl!

Text.SourceString: You'd be surprised how calming cooking can be. It's like yoga, but without all the poses.
Text.LocalizedString: You'd be surprised how calming cooking can be. It's like yoga, but without all the poses.

Text.SourceString: Cultivating glow algae is tricky.//Oh, that's a diva plant. Get your soil and sand mix just a tad off, and poof! Wilt city.
Text.LocalizedString: Cultivating glow algae is tricky.//Oh, that's a diva plant. Get your soil and sand mix just a tad off, and poof! Wilt city.

Text.SourceString: My garden is my little escape pod. Perfect spot for daydreaming, pondering life, and dodging the village's latest gossip.
Text.LocalizedString: My garden is my little escape pod. Perfect spot for daydreaming, pondering life, and dodging the village's latest gossip.

Text.SourceString: Nothing like waking up to the scent of fresh blooming sea roses.
Text.LocalizedString: Nothing like waking up to the scent of fresh blooming sea roses.

Text.SourceString: Well, maybe waking up to the sun shining...yeah? I can't even imagine how you land-dwellers handle that heat.//Do you actually enjoy that?
Text.LocalizedString: Well, maybe waking up to the sun shining...yeah? I can't even imagine how you land-dwellers handle that heat.//Do you actually enjoy that?

Text.SourceString: There's this stubborn coral patch that won't grow. Got any tips?
Text.LocalizedString: There's this stubborn coral patch that won't grow. Got any tips?

Text.SourceString: Have you heard about the Princess' new collection?//Door frames, was it? Let's just say it's making quite the splash around here.
Text.LocalizedString: Have you heard about the Princess' new collection?//Door frames, was it? Let's just say it's making quite the splash around here.

Text.SourceString: You should've seen the mess <NPCName>Denali</> made when she first tried crafting. Glittery seaweed everywhere.
Text.LocalizedString: You should've seen the mess <NPCName>Denali</> made when she first tried crafting. Glittery seaweed everywhere.

Text.SourceString: I've got this little patch of moonlit corals. They only bloom during the full moon.//So, tell me. You ever have plants that prefer the moon to the sun?
Text.LocalizedString: I've got this little patch of moonlit corals. They only bloom during the full moon.//So, tell me. You ever have plants that prefer the moon to the sun?

Text.SourceString: Talk about a real test of patience...trying to keep those pesky seahorses from munching on my kelp greens.
Text.LocalizedString: Talk about a real test of patience...trying to keep those pesky seahorses from munching on my kelp greens.

Text.SourceString: I need to talk to <NPCName>Slamet</> about it. He's not stern enough with those sea horses.
Text.LocalizedString: I need to talk to <NPCName>Slamet</> about it. He's not stern enough with those sea horses.

Text.SourceString: Tried a new hybrid sea-fern. Was hoping for a sparkly blue, got more of a loud green.//Oh, well, adds character.
Text.LocalizedString: Tried a new hybrid sea-fern. Was hoping for a sparkly blue, got more of a loud green.//Oh, well, adds character.

Text.SourceString: Saw <NPCName>Rysy</> and <NPCName>Olan</> at near the Kingdom yesterday. Not talking, just...floating.//Trouble in paradise or just a silent disco?
Text.LocalizedString: Saw <NPCName>Rysy</> and <NPCName>Olan</> at near the Kingdom yesterday. Not talking, just...floating.//Trouble in paradise or just a silent disco?

Text.SourceString: Did you hear the chatter at the market? Someone found an antique trident they're claiming is King Neptune's!
Text.LocalizedString: Did you hear the chatter at the market? Someone found an antique trident they're claiming is King Neptune's!

Text.SourceString: But I have my doubts, I think it's just old decor from a shipwreck. It's missing that certain 'oomph' factor, you know?
Text.LocalizedString: But I have my doubts, I think it's just old decor from a shipwreck. It's missing that certain 'oomph' factor, you know?

Text.SourceString: Ever hear about <NPCName>Olan</>'s secret seaweed stash? He's got flavors I didn’t even know existed.
Text.LocalizedString: Ever hear about <NPCName>Olan</>'s secret seaweed stash? He's got flavors I didn’t even know existed.

Text.SourceString: Jellyfish stings are the talk of the town. Either we've got a bloom situation or it's a new beauty trend I'm unaware of.
Text.LocalizedString: Jellyfish stings are the talk of the town. Either we've got a bloom situation or it's a new beauty trend I'm unaware of.

Text.SourceString: My first crafting attempt? Aimed for a necklace, landed on a tiara. Wore it all day and made everyone call me 'Your Highness'. Ha!
Text.LocalizedString: My first crafting attempt? Aimed for a necklace, landed on a tiara. Wore it all day and made everyone call me 'Your Highness'. Ha!

Text.SourceString: Ever tried mixing coffee and saltwater? I did. Spoiler alert: it's a no-go.//Some dreams just aren’t meant to be brewed.
Text.LocalizedString: Ever tried mixing coffee and saltwater? I did. Spoiler alert: it's a no-go.//Some dreams just aren’t meant to be brewed.

Text.SourceString: Took a 'me-time' trip into a cave and got lost. Boom! Stumbled upon a secret coral garden.//Can't find it again, though. Oh well.
Text.LocalizedString: Took a 'me-time' trip into a cave and got lost. Boom! Stumbled upon a secret coral garden.//Can't find it again, though. Oh well.

Text.SourceString: Float-yoga is harder than it looks. Trust me!//<portrait=normal>It's like levitation, but with a splash of meditation.
Text.LocalizedString: Float-yoga is harder than it looks. Trust me!//<portrait=normal>It's like levitation, but with a splash of meditation.

Text.SourceString: I see the 'twisted fin' hairstyle is back...Wore that in my teens. Everything old is new again, I suppose.
Text.LocalizedString: I see the 'twisted fin' hairstyle is back...Wore that in my teens. Everything old is new again, I suppose.

Text.SourceString: Heard of the new seaweed diet? Apparently, it’s all about balance. One week green, one week red.//I should give it a go.
Text.LocalizedString: Heard of the new seaweed diet? Apparently, it’s all about balance. One week green, one week red.//I should give it a go.

Text.SourceString: Have you heard the song of the humpback whales? It’s the serenade of the deep. Nothing quite like it.
Text.LocalizedString: Have you heard the song of the humpback whales? It’s the serenade of the deep. Nothing quite like it.

Text.SourceString: I wonder what <NPCName>Tahat</> is up to tomorrow. Maybe we can head up and catch the sunset. Just the two of us, without <NPCName>Denali</>. A little mom and dad time, ah ha!
Text.LocalizedString: I wonder what <NPCName>Tahat</> is up to tomorrow. Maybe we can head up and catch the sunset. Just the two of us, without <NPCName>Denali</>. A little mom and dad time, ah ha!

Text.SourceString: Whipped up a seaweed casserole today. If it's a hit, it'll be on the weekly menu; if not, well, we'll just call it 'experimental'.
Text.LocalizedString: Whipped up a seaweed casserole today. If it's a hit, it'll be on the weekly menu; if not, well, we'll just call it 'experimental'.

Text.SourceString: Ran into a school of fish today. Literally. I swear they change directions more often than I change my mind!
Text.LocalizedString: Ran into a school of fish today. Literally. I swear they change directions more often than I change my mind!

Text.SourceString: <NPCName>Denali</>, her dad and I had a movie night. Well, more like we made up stories while watching the currents.
Text.LocalizedString: <NPCName>Denali</>, her dad and I had a movie night. Well, more like we made up stories while watching the currents.
